name: Strings
description:
The first collector of this NFT will receive this original painting. 1st collector, please DM me via Twitter @Maks_Denysenko & I'll send you the painting!
 
Strings
Always interesting processes on the verge of conscious and unconscious, nature and culture. For example, automatic writing, deep trance, and even everyday things. While preparing for the exam, I was a little distracted, returned to the list of questions and noticed that my hand on the pen points to the very question I was focusing on. I didn't even have time to analyze what the last question was about, and my unconscious immediately presented the decision. Something similar happens when I write pictures, the main thing is to let it happen!

Artwork created by Maksym Denysenko in 2019, spray paint on canvas, 90x90 cm, 8023x7861 pix.
